@actnowforward @GDW001 @Renew2O22 @RachelBitecofer @KimReynoldsIA Did you watch the State of the Union address last night?

There were 600 people crammed into a room the size of a gymnasium, most of whom were over 60 years old, including the President and the Speaker if the House who are 79 and 81 who were four feet apart.

No one wore a mask.
